A '''Stark guard''' is a recurring background character in the [[Season 2|second season]]. He is played by Irish actor/extra Colin McMurray and debuts in &quot;[[The Old Gods and the New]].&quot; He is a [[House Stark]] guardsman fighting for King [[Robb Stark]] in the [[War of the Five Kings]].

