sections.Biography:
===[[Season 2]]===
He is a House Stark guardsman fighting for King [[Robb Stark]] in the [[War of the Five Kings]]. He is congratulated by Robb for having taken a [[House Lannister|Lannister]] helm.&lt;ref&gt;&quot;[[The Old Gods and the New]]&quot;&lt;/ref&gt;

He is present when Ser [[Jaime Lannister]] is recaptured and defends the prisoner against a vengeful Lord [[Rickard Karstark]].&lt;ref&gt;&quot;[[A Man Without Honor]]&quot;&lt;/ref&gt;
